.................... // Configures the DMA buffer to use the ECAN Peripheral 
.................... //    Transmit CAN1 set to DMA Channel 0 
.................... //    Receive CAN1 set to DMA Channel 1 
.................... //    Transmit CAN2 set to DMA Channel 2 
.................... //    Receive CAN2 set to DMA Channel 3 
.................... //        
.................... //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// 
